    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Places on land, beside a body of water, where fishermen gather or otherwise from which fishing is practiced. For hydrographic features where fishing is done offshore, use "fishing areas."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
